Thanks for the feedback! If your issue is related to the Flutter framework itself,
please open an issue at
[github.com/flutter/flutter](https://github.com/flutter/flutter/issues/new).

Please file this bug report at https://github.com/flutter/flutter-intellij/issues/new.

---

## What happened

Just setting everything up

## Version information

Android Studio `3.2.1` • Flutter plugin `io.flutter 31.3.1` • Dart plugin `181.5656`

Flutter 1.0.0 • channel stable • https://github.com/flutter/flutter.git
Framework • revision 5391447fae (3 weeks ago) • 2018-11-29 19:41:26 -0800
Engine • revision 7375a0f414
Tools • Dart 2.1.0 (build 2.1.0-dev.9.4 f9ebf21297)

_Please tell us what you were doing and what went wrong_
